ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great intro to using the SCID

This course acquaints you with the SCID and gives you confidence before completing intakes in the clinic. When you take this course, think critically and really get your practice because it will only benefit you!

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Great intro to a major diagnostic tool
Increased knowledge of interviewing. This is important for both research and practice, both of which I will do.

This course was expertly paired with our Advanced Psychopathology course. We were given the opportunity to complete several assignments to deepen our understanding of diagnostic assessments, and we were given ample opportunities to practice.
